measurements.description: Thirty-nine flowers and two buds on five arching to pendulous inflorescences; dorsal sepal hooded, yellow heavily ovelaid and blotched dark brown-burgundy; lateral sepals lanceolate, yellow, very heavily ovelaid and blotched dark brown-burgundy; petals lanceolate, reflexed, yellow very heavily ovelaid and blotched dark brown-burgundy coalescing centrally; lip pale yellow, blotched dark burgundy; column light yellow spotted burgundy, overlaid burgundy distally, anther cap cream; substance firm; texture matte.
